title: Highlights from Cal’s podium session at Pac-12 Media Day
text:
Photo: Jeff Chiu / Associated Press California head coach Cuonzo Martin, right, speaks next to Tyrone Wallace during NCAA college basketball Pac-12 media day in San Francisco, Thursday, Oct. 15, 2015. (AP Photo/Jeff Chiu) California head coach Cuonzo Martin, right, speaks next to Tyrone...
The overarching story line at the center of Cal’s nine-minute session at the Pac-12 Media Day podium was hardly a surprise: How are the Bears handling heightened outside expectations?
